library ExampleMeasure version '0.0.001'

using QDM version '5.4'

codesystem "SNOMEDCT:2018-03": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96' version 'urn:hl7:version:2018-03'
codesystem "SNOMEDCT": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96'
codesystem "LOINC:2.52": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.1' version 'urn:hl7:version:2.52'

valueset "High-Risk Medications With Days Supply Criteria": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.196.12.1254'

code "Breast cancer genetic marker of susceptibility positive (finding)": '445333001' from "SNOMEDCT:2018-03" display 'Breast cancer genetic marker of susceptibility positive (finding)'
code "Computer record of patient (record artifact)": '184225006' from "SNOMEDCT" display 'Computer record of patient (record artifact)'
code "Faxed report (record artifact)": '445666005' from "SNOMEDCT" display 'Faxed report (record artifact)'
code "Pediatric oncologist (occupation)": '309336000' from "SNOMEDCT:2018-03" display 'Pediatric oncologist (occupation)'
code "PHQ-9 quick depression assessment panel [Reported.PHQ]": '44249-1' from "LOINC:2.52" display 'PHQ-9 quick depression assessment panel [Reported.PHQ]'
code "Primary care provider (occupation)": '453231000124104' from "SNOMEDCT" display 'Primary care provider (occupation)'
code "Residential environment (environment)": '272497004' from "SNOMEDCT" display 'Residential environment (environment)'

context Patient

define "Initial Population":
	exists ( ["Assessment, Order": "PHQ-9 quick depression assessment panel [Reported.PHQ]"] )
		or exists ( ["Communication, Performed": "Breast cancer genetic marker of susceptibility positive (finding)"] Comm
				where Comm.sender ~ "Pediatric oncologist (occupation)"
					and Comm.recipient ~ "Primary care provider (occupation)"
					and Comm.category ~ "Computer record of patient (record artifact)"
					and Comm.medium ~ "Faxed report (record artifact)"
		)
		or exists ( ["Medication, Order": "High-Risk Medications With Days Supply Criteria"] Med
				where Med.setting ~ "Residential environment (environment)"
		)
